{"tid":799226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 貴州織金拆僭起衝突 死咗3個(或以上)\"執法人員\" 多人入廠","createTime":"2018-08-30T01:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T01:58:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce7e7e3e9239457b87d117da7e99ec700dd4e2b","tid":799226,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:47:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>明報版本</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n貴州拆僭建   村民駕車撞執法人員3死10傷 (22:37)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180829/s00004/3c131f32a1be58c182cfcaadd86ef75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180829%2Fs00004%2F3c131f32a1be58c182cfcaadd86ef75b.jpg&h=3c3b1dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貴州畢節市織金縣今早發生一宗駕車故意撞人案，織金縣規劃執法大隊在拆除僭建時，一名村民與工作人員發生語言和肢體衝突，之後駕駛越野車撞向執法隊工作人員，2人當場死亡，1人傷重不治，另有7名工作人員和3名村民受傷。該村民已經被捕。<br />\n<br />\n織金縣政府網站傍晚通報事件，指今日上午10時許，織金縣規劃執法大隊在大寨安置點拆除違章建築物。在現場圍觀的一名姓劉織金縣大寨村村民，與工作人員發生語言和肢體衝突，劉駕駛一輛越野車撞向執法隊工作人員，導致2名工作人員當場死亡，1名工作人員送院搶救後不治，另7名工作人員和3名圍觀群眾受傷，全部傷者仍需留院。劉已被警方拘捕。織金縣政府強調，劉並非被拆僭建的當事人，當時是在現場圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的短片可見，執法隊員原本有十多人，衝撞過後，傷者躺倒在地，表情痛苦，旁人則上前攙扶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00004/1535551600112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00004%2F1535551600112&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=8ffded33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00004%2F1535551600112&h=1f3e43d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00004/1535551600112</a>"},{"pid":"4c01c56d3c55631fdb7f92d347f09a7f7b30dcb3","tid":799226,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"鬼國日常"},{"pid":"c77c3aeda02e02b79354a8a5969cf11df946bc56","tid":799226,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"被農民打死五個。貴州織金幾個小時前發生，規劃局和武警執法拆違建房。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034728701311643649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034728701311643649&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=4364e3f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034728701311643649&h=cd127af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034728701311643649</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034733089723805696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034733089723805696&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ca4e2f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034733089723805696&h=f38ee1b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034733089723805696</a><br />\n<br />\n貴州織金農民打死人第三季。隱約可以聽見哭聲，打死人，規劃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034753369422716928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034753369422716928&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=bfbe8874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034753369422716928&h=52a2f1a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034753369422716928</a><br />\n<br />\n貴州織金死人第四季。大寨那地方的安置房因老百姓在三樓頂上把邊圍一個女兒牆，然而規劃局就組織城管及派出所的來就打人，然後老百姓打不過就開著車直衝猛打，當場就死五人，有三人是規劃局的，有一人是駐村派出所的，有一個是老百姓，其中有一個是女的。還有十多人在醫院搶救。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034786043759718401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034786043759718401&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=680b1a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034786043759718401&h=bd250fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034786043759718401</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034786406604795905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034786406604795905&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=6dfc0992\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034786406604795905&h=ad18c3b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034786406604795905</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034792586689400838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034792586689400838&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=86f4ecd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034792586689400838&h=317c92bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034792586689400838</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034793618408534016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034793618408534016&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b54e7055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1034793618408534016&h=78141fcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1034793618408534016</a>"},{"pid":"c2bed57b29bc7542f65f896a6f01b997b257848c","tid":799226,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:50:47.000Z","msg":"【大紀元2018年08月30日訊】（大紀元記者顧曉華採訪報導）8月29日，貴州畢節市織金縣大寨村村民與「執法」人員激戰，雙方均有人員死傷，3死10傷，同時一名村民開車衝撞對方，撞人者與現場多名村民被警方抓捕。現場目擊者披露真實情況。<br />\n<br />\n據該縣政府網站公告稱，8月29日上午10時許，織金縣規劃監察大隊在織普高速東出口大寨安置點執法活動，現場圍觀的織金縣雙堰街道大寨村村民劉某某與工作人員發生語言和肢體衝突。之後，劉某某駕駛一輛越野車向工作人員進行衝撞，導致2名工作人員當場死亡，1名工作人員經送醫院搶救無效後死亡，7名工作人員和3名圍觀村民受傷。<br />\n<br />\n一名現場目擊者則向大紀元記者表示，官方報導歪曲事實，讓他實在看不下去，「他們可能騙得了網友，騙得了別人，但是我們織金大部分人都知道真相。」他向記者透露了現場情況。<br />\n<br />\n上午10時許，一大批「執法」人員要拆村民的房子，因為政府只允許村民建3層樓的房子，但是他們建了4層，因此稱其為違建要強拆，當然會遭到村民的阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n這位目擊者表示，「執法」人員與劉某某發生口角，對方先動手毆打劉某某，將其打暈，並且有一名帶頭人員喊：「打，打死我負責。」隨後村民起來反抗，雙方激戰。<br />\n<br />\n「當時那場面，長這麼大，電視裡面都看不見的畫面呀！鋼管、鐵鍬、木棒&hellip;&hellip;拿到什麼就用什麼打，雙方都是撿東西打。」他當時嚇得不敢上前。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友在微博評論上表示，「為什麼不提劉某父母先被當場打成重傷，後劉某趕至後又再次被打的事。」<br />\n<br />\n還有網友稱劉某某的妻子被當場打死。目擊者表示，打死的是不是劉某某的妻子不清楚，現場有一名女子被打死，他親眼所見現場有3人當場死亡，包括村民和執法人員。<br />\n<br />\n「當時已經死的死、傷的傷，村民們都紅眼了，一心就想打死那個說『打，打死我負責』的那個頭。」目擊者說。<br />\n<br />\n他還透露，劉某某被打暈醒來之後，開著車撞向那名帶頭的人，因為那名帶頭人看事情不對勁，想開車逃跑，劉某某開車撞過去，將其逼停。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者說：「現場死的都是打死的，劉某某開車怎麼可能撞自己村裡面的人。」<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，之後來了大批警察，將參與打架的村民都抓走，而且不允許圍觀村民拍照，誰拍照就將其手機摔壞。受傷的人送到縣醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n此事件在網絡上引起熱議，許多網友都同情村民，一位網友說：「本人不贊同暴力強拆，也不贊同暴力抗法，但是我贊同百姓都要有血性。」<br />\n<br />\n網友們認為，如果劉某某不是被逼到迫不得已，誰會做這種事？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/8/29/n10676758.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F8%2F29%2Fn10676758.htm&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=29abc5a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/8/29/n10676758.htm</a>"},{"pid":"63ee96e39975707659efbf06998050fcedeb3199","tid":799226,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"貴州湖南專出土匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a93251d805a86edb99133b5541c12ae9d992c3","tid":799226,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:58:05.000Z","msg":"本是同根生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}